These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, romance
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | romance |
| Transport     | helicopter | jet-ski  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, blueberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, weightlifting
1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | watermelon      | blueberry         |
| Sport   | cycling | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola
There 2 different types of food: peas, pumpkin
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | cola | fanta   |
| Food       | pumpkin  | peas |

 #################################

 
